><td><div><p>Light Scatter, Nephelometry</p>\n</div></td><td>14338</td><td>active</td><td/><td/></tr><tr><td>1</td><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">0260<a name=\"v3-ObservationMethod-0260\"> </a></td><td>IgE immunoassay antibody</td><td><div><p>Immunoassay, IgE Antibody Test</p>\n</div></td><td>14339</td><td>active</td><td/><td/></tr><tr><td>1</td><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">0261<a name=\"v3-ObservationMethod-0261\"> </a></td><td>Lymphocyte Microcytotoxicity Assay</td><td><div><p>Lymphocyte Microcytotoxicity Assay</p>\n</div></td><td>14340</td><td>active</td><td/><td/></tr><tr><td>1</td><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">0262<a name=\"v3-ObservationMethod-0262\"> </a></td><td>Spectrophotometry</td><td><div><p>Spectrophotometry</p>\n</div></td><td>14341</td><td>active</td><td/><td/></tr><tr><td>1</td><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">0263<a name=\"v3-ObservationMethod-0263\"> </a></td><td>Atomic absorption spectrophotometry (AAS)</td><td><div><p>Spectrophotometry, Atomic Absorption</p>\n</div></td><td>14342</td><td>active</td><td/><td/></tr><tr><td>1</td><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">0264<a name=\"v3-ObservationMethod-0264\"> </a></td><td>Ion selective electrode (ISE)</td><td><div><p>Electrochemical, Ion Selective Electrode</p>\n</div></td><td>14343</td><td>active</td><td/><td/></tr><tr><td>1</td><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">0265<a name=\"v3-ObservationMethod-0265\"> </a></td><td>Gas chromatography (GC)</td><td><div><p>Chromatography, Gas</p>\n</div></td><td>14344</td><td>active</td><td/><td/></tr><tr><td>1</td><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">0266<a name=\"v3-ObservationMethod-0266\"> </a></td><td>Isoelectric focusing (IEF)</td><td><div><p>Isoelectric Focusing</p>\n</div></td><td>14345</td><td>active</td><td/><td/></tr><tr><td>1</td><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">0267<a name=\"v3-ObservationMethod-0267\"> </a></td><td>Immunochemiluminescence</td><td><div><p>Immunoassay, Chemiluminescent</p>\n</div></td><td>14346</td><td>active</td><td/><td/></tr><tr><td>1</td><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">0268<a name=\"v3-ObservationMethod-0268\"> </a></td><td>Microparticle enzyme immunoassay (MEIA)</td><td><div><p>Immunoassay, Microparticle Enzyme</p>\n</div></td><td>14347</td><td>active</td><td/><td/></tr><tr><td>1</td><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">0269<a name=\"v3-ObservationMethod-0269\"> </a></td><td>ICP/MS</td><td><div><p>Inductively-Coupled Plasma/Mass Spectrometry</p>\n</div></td><td>14348</td><td>active</td><td/><td/></tr><tr><td>1</td><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">0270<a name=\"v3-ObservationMethod-0270\"> </a></td><td>Immunoradiometric assay (IRMA)</td><td><div><p>Immunoassay, Immunoradiometric Assay</p>\n</div></td><td>14349</td><td>active</td><td/><td/></tr><tr><td>1</td><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">0271<a name=\"v3-ObservationMethod-0271\"> </a></td><td>Photo optical clot detection</td><td><div><p>Coagulation, Photo Optical Clot Detection</p>\n</div></td><td>14350</td><td>active</td><td/><td/></tr><tr><td>1</td><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">0280<a name=\"v3-ObservationMethod-0280\"> </a></td><td>Susceptibility Testing</td><td><div><p>Test methods designed to determine a microorganismaTMs susceptibility to being killed by an antibiotic.</p>\n</div></td><td>21454</td><td>active</td><td/><td/></tr><tr><td>2</td><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">  0240<a name=\"v3-ObservationMethod-0240\"> </a></td><td>Antibiotic sensitivity, disk</td><td><div><p>Susceptibility, Antibiotic sensitivity, disk</p>\n</div></td><td>14319</td><td>active</td><td/><td/></tr><tr><td>2</td><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">  0241<a name=\"v3-ObservationMethod-0241\"> </a></td><td>BACTEC susceptibility test</td><td><div><p>Susceptibility, BACTEC susceptibility test</p>\n</div></td><td>14320</td><td>active</td><td/><td/></tr><tr><td>2</td><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">  0242<a name=\"v3-ObservationMethod-0242\"> </a></td><td>Disk dilution</td><td><div><p>Susceptibility, Disk dilution</p>\n</div></td><td>14321</td><td>active</td><td/><